a href=\"/index.php/Orkmont\" title=\"Orkmont\">Orkmont</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Successors</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Erich_I_Greyiron\" title=\"Erich I Greyiron\">Erich I Greyiron</a> (briefly)</li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Regnar_Drumm\" title=\"Regnar Drumm\">Regnar Drumm</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Personal Information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Aliases</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li>Ironfoot<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_driftwood_crowns.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_driftwood_crowns.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li><li>Urras Ironfoot<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_driftwood_crowns.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_driftwood_crowns.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Orkmont\" title=\"Orkmont\">Orkmont</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Dynasty</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Greyiron\" title=\"House Greyiron\">House Greyiron</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Erich_I_Greyiron\" title=\"Erich I Greyiron\">Erich I Greyiron</a><br />Son(s)</td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Rise_of_the_Dragon\" title=\"The Rise of the Dragon\">The Rise of the Dragon</a></i> (mentioned)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Urras Greyiron</b>, known as <b>Urras Ironfoot</b>, was a <a href=\"/index.php/High_King_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"High King of the Iron Islands\">High King of the Iron Islands</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Greyiron\" title=\"House Greyiron\">House Greyiron</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc1.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character\">Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Urras_Greyiron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Urras was the greatest reaver of his age.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_driftwood_crowns.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_driftwood_crowns.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Urras_Greyiron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The prophet <a href=\"/index.php/Galon_Whitestaff\" title=\"Galon Whitestaff\">Galon Whitestaff</a> summoned the numerous <a href=\"/index.php/Rock_king\" title=\"Rock king\">rock</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Salt_king\" title=\"Salt king\">salt kings</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Wyk\" title=\"Old Wyk\">Old Wyk</a> for a <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsmoot\" title=\"Kingsmoot\">kingsmoot</a>, during which Urras, the salt king of <a href=\"/index.php/Orkmont\" title=\"Orkmont\">Orkmont</a>, was chosen as the first <a href=\"/index.php/High_King_of_the_Iron_Islands\" title=\"High King of the Iron Islands\">High King of the Iron Islands</a>. Urras was the first monarch to rule all <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> since the <a href=\"/index.php/Grey_King\" title=\"Grey King\">Grey King</a>. After Ironfoot's death, the driftwood crown was claimed by his son, <a href=\"/index.php/Erich_I_Greyiron\" title=\"Erich I Greyiron\">Erich the Ugly</a>. Galon forced Erich to step down under threat of death, however, since he had not been chosen in a kingsmoot. <a href=\"/index.php/Regnar_Drumm\" title=\"Regnar Drumm\">Regnar Drumm</a> was instead chosen in a new kingsmoot.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_driftwood_crowns.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_iron_islands:_driftwood_crowns.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-edits